data.description: MAJOR PRICE IMPROVEMENT!! LOOK AT THESE VIEWS!!!! PANAMA COUNTRY CLUB, WATERFRONT, GULF ACCESS!!! Designed  for entertaining! This Country Club home features a spacious Family Room with a wet bar, and a wall of windows.... AMAZING Scenery!! Living Room has a cozy fireplace and built-in cabinetry. Kitchen is PERFECT for cookie making.....lots of granite counter space! There is an abundance of natural lighting to enjoy on a daily basis. The freshly painted large deck overlooks a peaceful lagoon teeming with wildlife. Dock has been recently replaced, and jet ski lift works. Location is bomb diggity - newly designed Country Club golf course, community pool, and of course shopping is close by! Please contact your favorite Realtor to see this one and only ....you are going to LOVE IT!! Buyer to confirm all information. Dining room table can convey, hot tub does not.
